OL,3,CUnpaid clean air zone fines reach #32m
OL,4,Cas council faces funding shortfall
OL,6,FBristol City Council is owed #229
OL,7,Fmillion in unpaid debt, including
OL,8,Fnearly #52 million worth of council
OL,9,Ftax.
OL,11,FNew figures reveal that as of 31 March
OL,12,F2024 there was #32 million in unpaid
OL,13,FClean Air Zone fines and almost #19
OL,14,Fmillion in overpaid housing benefits
OL,15,Fwhich had not been recovered.
