OL,4,Cas council faces funding shortfall
OL,6,FIt comes after council leader Cllr
OL,7,FTony Dyer warned that the organisation
OL,8,Ffollow other local authorities,
OL,9,Fincluding Birmingham and Nottingham,
OL,10,Fin effectively declaring bankruptcy if
OL,11,Fit could not find savings to plug a
OL,12,F#22 million budget shortfall this year.
OL,14,FThe report showed the reasons debt had
OL,15,Faccumulated included the fact bills in
OL,16,FBristol were higher than the national
OL,17,Faverage, additional reminder notices
OL,18,Fwhich meant unpaid cases took longer
OL,19,Fto progress, and court backlogs which
OL,20,Fmade it difficult to obtain time
OL,21,Fbefore magistrates.
