OL,6,FThe report said: "Cost of living
OL,7,Fpressures are clearly continuing to
OL,8,Fimpact and we are endeavouring to
OL,9,Fmaximise the support we are able to
OL,10,Foffer through new initiatives and
OL,11,Fprocesses.
OL,13,F"The 'premium rate' telephone line for
OL,14,Fpayments has been replaced, making
OL,15,Fcalls to this line more affordable.
