OL,6,F"The debt support referral service
OL,7,Fallows customer-facing teams across
OL,8,Fthe council to refer those struggling
OL,9,Fwith unmanageable debt, and who often
OL,10,Fhave other non-financial problems, for
OL,11,Fsupport, advice and signposting.
OL,13,F"We hold regular debt clinics around
OL,14,Fthe city targeting those living in the
OL,15,Flocality where our records indicate
OL,16,Funmanageable debts exist."
